{"tid":1268644,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"手足請入!我地要以其人之道還治其人之身!!","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:32.000Z","uid":65297,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05c3f9db1c1067711b37e871e72884206cdbd476","tid":1268644,"uid":65297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"手足聽我講 我地一定要冷靜<br />\n一直以黎我地都係用和平既手法去堅持<br />\n今日一班廢老藍絲走出黎攪事<br />\n係令到我地好憤怒 <br />\n但我想大家都諗清楚 <br />\n係咪我地call多d人出黎就解決到<br />\n<br />\n唔係囉 因為對方可能有黑底混入黎打人<br />\n我地唔可以再有人損傷<br />\n反而我覺得係依 d時候要用智力取勝<br />\n我地同廢老藍絲既分別係我地聰明有腦<br />\n<br />\n班廢老既然都係為錢出黎撐警<br />\n點解唔用同一種方法tum佢地出黎<br />\n豬隊友愈多愈好<br />\n做到幾大龍鳳都好<br />\n整到周街垃圾 衝馬路 <br />\n最好攪到連警察都反佢地感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VibU95T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVibU95T.jpg&h=efbdb6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之於召集人就搜羅網上見到既<br />\nwhatspp傳出黎既<br />\n佢地要人就幫佢叫多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢地估唔到人有噤多 錢又唔夠分<br />\n最後就會好多行完無錢手<br />\n等無腦又貪錢既廢老中伏<br />\n<br />\n我地玩多佢地幾次<br />\n就唔會再噤多廢老上當<br />\n班建制既朵都臭埋<br />\n<br />\n撐警遊行人多極都唔會多過200萬人<br />\n光環比一次佢地又點話<br />\n反而我地就要襯依d機會 <br />\n等班豬隊友出多d醜 <br />\n班hihi蠢到上癮攪記者攪後生仔<br />\n班黑警都照幫  一定有反效果!<br />\n<br />\n記住 我地要諗清楚先行動!<br />\n不受傷 不流血 一個都不能少!"},{"pid":"35dcde34b396bdbe2b1ac88534a9416fcdfb402b","tid":1268644,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3f432e8bbaeeba7e5fec5c0e537d11a87d3f96","tid":1268644,"uid":105879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"971619804f9aa0ce90295338f86847841fd52434","tid":1268644,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">相信七一係最後一次機會可以號召咁多人，我有小小嘢想講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"701e293e000ebbbfd29a49b9d0aa6b9cbbd11d33","tid":1268644,"uid":65297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13a284c45f71d8c91a8604a7aa59d592751968fc","tid":1268644,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9249e6cd58d0a8ad07dade636aa82a307208a4e","tid":1268644,"uid":271786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"香討都俾藍絲洗晒版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}